    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minimal wear on the driver's seat. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and some light surface scratches near the door handles. It\u2019s a dependable and well-cared-for car that is ready for its next owner.",
