      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in showroom condition, exhibiting zero discernible wear and absolute mechanical integrity. A definitive acquisition for the discerning driver who demands excellence without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
